               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1063" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1063" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1063" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1063" type="given" value="ADOLPHUS"></interp>ADOLPHUS TAYLOR</persName>
                  </hi>. I have been lodging with Mr. Green, in Stepney-fields—I was present in the Commercial-road, on the 4th of Aug., when Father Mathew was holding his meeting—I saw the prisoner go behind several gentlemen who were going to be pledged—I saw him go behind a gen<lb></lb>tleman, lift his coat, and put his hand in the pocket—there were three more with the prisoner who got round him—the prisoner then drew the handker<lb></lb>chief out of the prosecutor's pocket, and gave it to one of the three—the other</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184308210163"></xptr>
               <p>three ran away—I laid hold of the prisoner, called the police, and gave him into custody.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was right away down at the other end of the mob—you said to the gentleman "Did you lose a handkerchief?"—he said no at first, and then you said, "This is the boy that took it."</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1064" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1064" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1064" type="surname" value="WILLS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1064" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH WILLS</persName>
                  </hi>. I was on the ground—there was a great crowd—Taylor came and told me something, and I missed a silk pocket handkerchief, which had been in my pocket ten minutes before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was not near you when I was accused of this—I never saw it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
