                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1065" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT AYLIFFE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) The prisoner was given into my cus<lb></lb>tody—he said he knew nothing about it, and began to cry.</p>
